  "title": "📈 Events & Marketing (Clear Career Progression)",
  "description": "<p>If you’re tired of roles with no direction, this opportunity offers <strong>transparent, performance-based career progression</strong>.</p><p>Your growth is measured by effort and results — not seniority. You’ll start by learning event marketing and customer engagement, with clear pathways into leadership and management roles.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Ambitious individuals who want to see where their hard work leads.<br /><br /><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>🎯 Goal-oriented and ambitious mindset</li><li>💪 Strong work ethic and accountability</li><li>🧠 Coachable and open to feedback</li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>📢 Learn and apply ethical sales & marketing techniques</li><li>📊 Execute campaigns with clear performance goals</li><li>🚀 Progress into leadership roles based on results</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits / What You’ll Gain</strong></p><ul><li>📈 Transparent career pathway</li><li>👥 Leadership and management opportunities</li><li>🧩 Structured training and development</li></ul>",
